00:01:47,540 --> 00:01:50,510
What brings you to Zhen Tower, Sir Zang?

5
00:01:50,940 --> 00:01:54,920
I'm here to ask for a favor, Owner Xiang.

6
00:01:54,920 --> 00:01:57,950
The capital is holding the annual field hockey contest.

7
00:01:57,950 --> 00:02:00,480
The participants are sons from influential families.

8
00:02:00,480 --> 00:02:05,510
The imperial court's goal is to strengthen their bodies and encourage aspirations.

9
00:02:05,510 --> 00:02:09,020
The winner of each year will be rewarded by His Majesty.

10
00:02:09,020 --> 00:02:11,460
So? You want to participate, too?

11
00:02:11,460 --> 00:02:14,060
It's still not enough for you to impress the Marquis of Pingjin

12
00:02:14,060 --> 00:02:16,250
and you even want to gain His Majesty's attention?

13
00:02:16,250 --> 00:02:18,470
It's not me. I'm doing this for the

14
00:02:18,470 --> 00:02:20,460
Second Young Master of the Zhuang family.

15
00:02:20,460 --> 00:02:22,490
Him? Why?

16
00:02:22,490 --> 00:02:25,740
I want him to use this opportunity to shine.

17
00:02:25,740 --> 00:02:27,840
What happens after that?

18
00:02:27,840 --> 00:02:31,930
He'll become the son that the Marquis thinks highly of.

19
00:02:37,700 --> 00:02:40,210
Did I hear it wrong, Sir Zang?

20
00:02:40,210 --> 00:02:43,630
Have you lost your mind? Are you blind?

21
00:02:43,630 --> 00:02:45,940
I can find a physician to treat you.

22
00:02:46,470 --> 00:02:49,350
Owner Xiang, please sit.

23
00:02:53,460 --> 00:02:56,080
If one wants to survive and succeed in a powerful family,

24
00:02:56,080 --> 00:02:58,740
how can we just rely on only one person?

25
00:03:00,680 --> 00:03:02,260
Owner Xiang,

26
00:03:02,260 --> 00:03:05,360
