27
00:03:05,360 --> 00:03:07,350
Don't ask anymore.

28
00:03:08,420 --> 00:03:11,590
Speak. How can I help you?

29
00:03:11,590 --> 00:03:15,630
I need Eighth Young Master to drum up publicity for Zhuang Zhixing before the field hockey contest.

30
00:03:15,630 --> 00:03:17,370
I want everyone in the capital to know that

31
00:03:17,370 --> 00:03:21,030
Zhuang Zhixing is the younger version of the Marquis.

32
00:03:22,810 --> 00:03:23,900
Fine.

33
00:03:23,900 --> 00:03:27,580
There's no reason for Zhen Tower to decline this transaction.

34
00:03:35,520 --> 00:03:38,150
First, we need to change Zhuang Zhixing's image.

35
00:03:38,150 --> 00:03:40,590
This image of a useless idler won't do.

36
00:03:40,590 --> 00:03:44,620
He must be a stylish, energetic, and heroic son of an aristocrat.

37
00:03:44,620 --> 00:03:48,030
Zhen Tower will send people everywhere to spread good news about him.

38
00:03:48,030 --> 00:03:52,000
These people need money for expenses and legwork.

39
00:03:52,000 --> 00:03:54,750
It's at least three taels of silver per man per day.

40
00:03:54,750 --> 00:03:57,300
It's a big city. Based on 20 men,

41
00:03:57,300 --> 00:04:00,010
it's 60 taels of silver each day.

42
00:04:03,370 --> 00:04:08,020
But with your meager salary, I believe you can't afford it.

43
00:04:08,020 --> 00:04:10,830
You have to pawn something.

44
00:04:14,310 --> 00:04:18,950
The quality of this jade is too ordinary.

45
00:04:19,380 --> 00:04:21,630
At most, it's 20 taels of silver.

46
00:04:21,630 --> 00:04:23,580
This is still a small sum of money.

47
00:04:23,580 --> 00:04:25,730
If you want Eighth Young Master to personally do it,

48
00:04:25,730 --> 00:04:28,140
you must pay him 80 taels of silver for each shadow play performance.

49
00:04:28,140 --> 00:04:30,390
He needs to create a new shadow figure for Zhuang Zhixing.

50
00:04:30,390 --> 00:04:33,040
The total amount is 150 taels of silver.

51
00:04:33,040 --> 00:04:34,170
About the 150 taels of silver...

52
00:04:34,170 --> 00:04:36,190
Taking into account that we are friends,

53
00:04:36,190 --> 00:04:38,150
my offer is 120 taels of silver.

54
00:04:39,390 --> 00:04:40,950
Nice robe.

55
00:04:40,950 --> 00:04:42,580
A reward from the Marquis?

56
00:04:42,580 --> 00:04:44,600
Floating Light Brocade, great material.

57
00:04:44,600 --> 00:04:47,160
I will give you a further discount.

58
00:04:47,160 --> 00:04:48,870
Owner Xiang, you must be joking.

59
00:04:48,870 --> 00:04:51,530
If I pawn my robe, I have to leave naked.

60
00:04:51,530 --> 00:04:52,870
None of my business

61
00:04:52,870 --> 00:04:54,170
but it's not over yet.

62
00:04:54,170 --> 00:04:58,520
Wait till the contest starts on that day, this money will double.

63
00:04:58,520 --> 00:04:59,580
Sir Zang,

64
00:04:59,580 --> 00:05:04,080
after the contest ends, you'll still owe me.

65
00:05:04,080 --> 00:05:07,480
If you don't pay me, I'll collect the debt from your sons and grandsons.

66
00:05:07,480 --> 00:05:09,920
This money will roll and there will be compound interest.

67
00:05:09,920 --> 00:05:12,260
Your descendants will forever be in debt...

68
00:05:12,260 --> 00:05:13,680
Stop.

69
00:05:14,830 --> 00:05:16,100
Owner Xiang,

70
00:05:16,100 --> 00:05:18,950
as what you said, I can't cough up this sum of money

71
00:05:18,950 --> 00:05:24,570
but I've a way for you to profit from this sum of money.

72
00:05:25,190 --> 00:05:27,120
I'll give you this opportunity.

73
00:05:32,600 --> 00:05:36,980
Zhuang Zhixing has a bad reputation, but he's the second son of the Marquis.

74
00:05:36,980 --> 00:05:39,800
The affairs of the nobles, secrets of the rich and powerful families,

75
00:05:39,800 --> 00:05:41,390
if we let Eighth Young Second use them as gimmicks

76
00:05:41,390 --> 00:05:44,240
and based his play on them,

77
00:05:44,240 --> 00:05:47,090
people would swarm into the theater.

78
00:05:47,090 --> 00:05:49,310
Your collection from the ticket sales

79
00:05:49,310 --> 00:05:53,720
is at least 50 taels of silver each day.

80
00:05:53,720 --> 00:05:57,160
It's a total of 350 taels of silver for seven days.

81
00:05:57,160 --> 00:06:01,600
I heard Zhen Tower runs a betting pool for the annual field hockey contest.

82
00:06:01,600 --> 00:06:05,850
Few people will bet on an inexperienced rookie like him.

83
00:06:05,850 --> 00:06:07,800
However, if he turns out to be a dark horse,

84
00:06:07,800 --> 00:06:13,660
Zhen Tower will hit the jackpot and make a fortune out of it.

85
00:06:13,660 --> 00:06:18,000
You can make at least 400 taels of silver...

86
00:06:18,000 --> 00:06:19,850
no...

87
00:06:19,850 --> 00:06:21,020
500 taels of silver.

88
00:06:21,020 --> 00:06:24,090
- Your accounts... 
 - Let me finish talking.

89
00:06:25,070 --> 00:06:29,060
When the contest ends, Zhuang Zhixing will be famous.

90
00:06:29,060 --> 00:06:33,920
All the food that he ate, songs that he listened to,

91
00:06:33,920 --> 00:06:39,220
