239
00:22:40,880 --> 00:22:43,120
It's not surprising at all.

240
00:22:43,720 --> 00:22:48,030
He was hopelessly useless in the past and beyond help.

241
00:22:48,030 --> 00:22:50,900
Unexpectedly, he finally accomplished something.

242
00:22:52,000 --> 00:22:54,510
I didn't teach him in vain.

243
00:22:54,510 --> 00:22:57,550
The imperial court will reward the winner tomorrow.

244
00:22:57,550 --> 00:23:01,010
I heard the Imperial Eunuch holding the seal from the Directorate of Ceremonial will be there.

245
00:23:01,010 --> 00:23:02,620
Marquis, if you can't make it,

246
00:23:02,620 --> 00:23:06,130
I'd like to take some people with me to congratulate him.

247
00:23:08,590 --> 00:23:10,640
He's the winner.

248
00:23:10,640 --> 00:23:13,860
As his father, I have to support him in person.

249
00:23:13,860 --> 00:23:16,920
Also, officials from the imperial court will be present.

250
00:23:16,920 --> 00:23:20,030
Go with me tomorrow.

251
00:23:20,030 --> 00:23:21,960
You are my aide.

