You often hate to compete with others.

261
00:24:01,210 --> 00:24:03,590
Why do you suddenly like field hockey?

262
00:24:03,590 --> 00:24:05,240
I've grown up

263
00:24:05,240 --> 00:24:07,790
and want to share your burdens, just like my older brother.

264
00:24:07,790 --> 00:24:10,860
But I know my literary talent is not as good as his.

265
00:24:10,860 --> 00:24:12,400
I can only improve my martial arts

266
00:24:12,400 --> 00:24:14,510
to assist you in the future.

267
00:24:14,510 --> 00:24:20,000
I didn't expect you'd impress others if you kept quiet.

268
00:24:20,000 --> 00:24:23,200
It's your first time joining a contest, and you won.

269
00:24:23,200 --> 00:24:24,710
Well done.

270
00:24:25,620 --> 00:24:27,830
I've trained for only two months.

271
00:24:27,830 --> 00:24:31,160
I only wanted to play a few rounds for enjoyment.

272
00:24:31,160 --> 00:24:33,440
Who knew that after overcoming obstacles,

273
00:24:33,440 --> 00:24:35,750
it could be possible to win.

274
00:24:36,640 --> 00:24:38,880
You're my son.

275
00:24:38,880 --> 00:24:44,020
Generals run in the Zhuang family. It's in your blood.

276
00:24:45,490 --> 00:24:46,820
I'll remember this, Father.

277
00:24:46,820 --> 00:24:48,860
Fine. You can leave.

278
00:24:48,860 --> 00:24:52,250
Marquis, your son is talented.

279
00:24:52,250 --> 00:24:54,460
You're flattering me, Sir Lin.

280
00:24:55,270 --> 00:24:58,520
Eunuch Cao is here! 
    

281
00:25:53,510 --> 00:25:55,680
- Greetings, Eunuch Cao! 
 - Greetings, Eunuch Cao!

282
00:25:55,680 --> 00:26:00,320
Eunuch Cao, you're radiant and full of energy.

283
00:26:01,720 --> 00:26:04,750
Marquis, you are so blessed.

284
00:26:04,750 --> 00:26:06,680
Your elder son serves in the imperial court

285
00:26:06,680 --> 00:26:10,480
