289
00:26:18,760 --> 00:26:21,170
How is His Majesty lately?

290
00:26:21,170 --> 00:26:25,870
Thank you for your concern. His Majesty is fine.

291
00:26:27,200 --> 00:26:30,170
His Majesty mentioned you the day before yesterday.

292
00:26:30,170 --> 00:26:34,680
You should go to the palace more often.

293
00:26:34,680 --> 00:26:35,830
I will.

294
00:26:35,830 --> 00:26:39,000
Please thank His Majesty for his grace on my behalf.

295
00:26:39,000 --> 00:26:42,530
I'll wait for his summons to see me at any time.

296
00:26:51,160 --> 00:26:53,250
This is my newly recruited aide.

297
00:26:53,250 --> 00:26:56,780
Zang Hai, greet Eunuch Cao immediately.

298
00:26:58,270 --> 00:27:01,570
Greetings, Eunuch Cao.

299
00:27:02,200 --> 00:27:09,590
Are you the new geomancer hired by the Marquis

300
00:27:09,590 --> 00:27:12,160
