301
00:27:12,160 --> 00:27:18,160
Marquis and First Master Zhuang made the decision. I dare not take the credit.

302
00:27:20,270 --> 00:27:23,160
Marquis, how did you recruit such a gem?

303
00:27:23,160 --> 00:27:25,340
Why didn't you tell me about him?

304
00:27:25,340 --> 00:27:28,480
Are you afraid I might poach him?

305
00:27:28,480 --> 00:27:31,270
Eunuch Cao loves to joke.

306
00:27:31,270 --> 00:27:34,510
The Imperial Surveillance Office recruits talented people in the kingdom.

307
00:27:34,510 --> 00:27:38,190
My insignificant aide is no match for them.

308
00:27:41,160 --> 00:27:47,650
Although it's the first time we've met, there's a sense of familiarity.

309
00:27:49,000 --> 00:27:51,880
Sir, you assist His Majesty, who has many assistants

310
00:27:51,880 --> 00:27:53,960
and have met millions of people.

311
00:27:53,960 --> 00:27:56,680
I'm just an ordinary person.

312
00:27:56,680 --> 00:28:01,940
It's my honor that I can catch your attention.

313
00:28:03,350 --> 00:28:05,680
Well said.

314
00:28:05,680 --> 00:28:07,550
You're born to be eloquent.

315
00:28:07,550 --> 00:28:09,560
I like you.

316
00:28:10,200 --> 00:28:12,780
I've been feeling very bored recently.

317
00:28:12,780 --> 00:28:15,170
I lack someone

318
00:28:15,170 --> 00:28:17,750
who is smart and humorous.

319
00:28:17,750 --> 00:28:21,680
I wonder if the Marquis is willing to understand my loneliness

320
00:28:21,680 --> 00:28:24,070
and bear to part with this gem?

321
00:28:24,070 --> 00:28:26,000
Eunuch, don't say that.

322
00:28:26,000 --> 00:28:29,670
Among the attendants, civil and military officials in the imperial court,

323
00:28:29,670 --> 00:28:33,480
who can be more eloquent than you?

324
00:28:33,480 --> 00:28:38,040
Does this mean you refused my offer?

325
00:28:45,450 --> 00:28:49,570
Eunuch, everything's ready and waiting for you.

326
00:29:02,310 --> 00:29:04,430
This is His Majesty's oral decree.

327
00:29:06,060 --> 00:29:09,610
"I know that field hockey is loved by the people.

328
00:29:09,610 --> 00:29:11,960
The winners:

329
00:29:11,960 --> 00:29:16,270
Zhuang Zhixing, Mu Zhanqing, Jiang Yu, Sun Yongmin

330
00:29:16,270 --> 00:29:19,450
turned the tide and won my heart.

331
00:29:19,450 --> 00:29:22,250
I reward you with a magpie robe each."

332
00:29:22,250 --> 00:29:26,440
Eunuch Cao is unpredictable.

333
00:29:26,440 --> 00:29:29,030
He personally said he wanted you.

334
00:29:29,030 --> 00:29:33,600
Once you enter the Imperial Surveillance Office, you can't leave.

335
00:29:34,120 --> 00:29:37,410
Go to the treasury tomorrow to choose a few decent treasures

336
00:29:37,410 --> 00:29:39,510
and get someone to deliver them to his residence.

337
00:29:39,510 --> 00:29:41,240
Yes, Marquis.

338
00:29:41,240 --> 00:29:45,000
Tell the kitchen to cook a few of Zhixing's favorite dishes for dinner.

339
00:29:45,000 --> 00:29:48,280
He has worked hard for the past days.

340
00:29:49,160 --> 00:29:50,630
Understood.

341
00:30:10,000 --> 00:30:13,450
Zang Hai is a talented geomancer.

342
00:30:13,450 --> 00:30:17,680
However, I feel unsettled when I see him.

343
00:30:17,680 --> 00:30:20,160
Based on your friendship with the Marquis of Pingjin,

344
00:30:20,160 --> 00:30:22,790
