345
00:30:22,790 --> 00:30:26,000
Does he want to retain Zang Hai to make good use of him?

346
00:30:26,720 --> 00:30:28,920
Ten years have passed.

347
00:30:28,920 --> 00:30:32,340
Zhuang Luyin is still alive.

348
00:30:32,340 --> 00:30:35,760
Why do I feel nervous?

