367
00:32:28,550 --> 00:32:30,480
I didn't think he would go that far

368
00:32:30,480 --> 00:32:32,920
to actually request that he serve the Marquis of Pingjin.

369
00:32:32,920 --> 00:32:36,850
It's obvious he wants a meteoric rise and rapid promotion to become an official.

370
00:32:36,850 --> 00:32:40,900
Not only this, the first month he entered the Marquis Residence,

371
00:32:40,900 --> 00:32:43,920
