374
00:32:55,480 --> 00:32:59,550
Are you saying he has murderous intent?

375
00:32:59,550 --> 00:33:02,340
I accidentally offended him.

376
00:33:02,340 --> 00:33:05,160
I'm afraid I may be his next target.

377
00:33:05,160 --> 00:33:07,960
Eunuch, please protect me.

378
00:33:07,960 --> 00:33:11,160
I like the statue of Goddess of Mercy that you gifted me.

379
00:33:11,160 --> 00:33:14,200
I'll help you with the decision on this.

380
00:33:14,200 --> 00:33:16,250
Thank you, Eunuch.

381
00:33:16,250 --> 00:33:20,970
I'll find a better gift for your enjoyment.

382
00:33:20,970 --> 00:33:22,950
You are considerate.

383
00:33:34,550 --> 00:33:36,040
Lu Jin.

384
00:33:36,780 --> 00:33:38,270
Foster Father.

385
00:33:38,270 --> 00:33:40,250
Go to Qingquan Town immediately to probe.

386
00:33:40,250 --> 00:33:44,160
If there's a problem with his identity and, Zhuang Luyin wants to use him, he can't.

387
00:33:44,160 --> 00:33:46,030
- Go now. 
 - Understood.

388
00:33:46,030 --> 00:33:47,860
Lu Yan.

389
00:33:47,860 --> 00:33:50,250
Send people to keep a close eye on Zang Hai.

390
00:33:50,250 --> 00:33:53,550
Once Lu Jin finds out something suspicious about Zang Hai's identity,

391
00:33:53,550 --> 00:33:55,070
