How about this? I'll buy them all.

399
00:34:45,220 --> 00:34:47,130
It doesn't cost that much.

400
00:34:47,130 --> 00:34:49,360
Take it.

401
00:34:49,360 --> 00:34:52,010
- This... 
 - It's fine.

402
00:34:52,010 --> 00:34:53,840
I was about to ask you something.

403
