405
00:34:57,350 --> 00:34:58,880
I'm here to visit a relative.

406
00:34:58,880 --> 00:35:00,190
Which relative?

407
00:35:00,190 --> 00:35:02,800
I've lived here for decades.

408
00:35:02,800 --> 00:35:04,920
I know almost everyone.

409
00:35:04,920 --> 00:35:06,110
Perfect.

410
00:35:06,110 --> 00:35:08,010
Do you know Zang Hai?

411
