421
00:35:35,970 --> 00:35:39,840
There was a fire several months ago.

422
00:35:39,840 --> 00:35:41,630
The carpenter was burned alive.

423
00:35:41,630 --> 00:35:44,700
Xiao Hai was cutting wood in the mountains. He didn't go home

